v0.1 06nov2018
* Initial release

v0.2 29nov2018
* Temperature bug fixed

v0.3 02dec2018
* Now wind and wind gust data in m/s

v0.4 26mar2019
* Uploads rate limit added.
RP5-API requires no more than 60 r/m

v0.5 17mar2026
* Migrated to Python 3.
* Updated imports (urllib.request, queue).
* Replaced sys.maxint with sys.maxsize.
* Compatibility with WeeWX 4.x and 5.x.

v0.6 29mar2026
* Replaced syslog with Python logging module (WeeWX 5.x compatibility).
* API URL changed from HTTP to HTTPS.
* Added barometer (p0) and rain (rr) fields to uploaded data.
* Wind speed and gust precision increased from 0 to 1 decimal place.
* Removed dead Python 2 TypeError fallback in post_request.
* All HTTP errors now wrapped as FailedPost for uniform retry/backoff behaviour.
* Default timeout increased from 5s to 10s; default retry_wait from 2s to 5s.